
'''''Timbuktu''''' ni filime y’ikinamico ya Mauritanian-Igifaransa yakozwe  2014 iyobowe kandi yanditswe na Abderrahmane Sissako . Iyi filime yibanze ku bikorwa bigufi bya Timbuktu, muri [[Mali]] na Ansar Dine, kandi bigira uruhare runini mu gutera amabuye rusange mu mwaka wa 2012 abashakanye batashyingiranywe muri Aguelhok . Yafatiwe amashusho muri Oualata, muri [[Moritaniya|Mauritania]], ''Timbuktu'' yatoranijwe guhatanira Palme d'or mu gice cy’amarushanwa akomeye mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2014, aho yatsindiye igihembo cya Ecumenical ndetse n’igihembo cya François Chalais .    Yatoranijwe muri Mauritania ihatanira  igihembo cya Akademiki ya Filime Nziza Y’amahanga , ikomeza gutorwa itwara igihembo mu bihembo bya 87 bya Academy ; yatorewe kandi igihembo cya BAFTA igihembo cya Filime Nziza itari mu Cyongereza mu bihembo bya 69 bya British Academy Film Awards .   ''Timbuktu'' yahawe igihembo cya Filime nziza mu bihembo bya 11 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards, aho yatorewe ibindi bihembo icumi.  Muri 2017, ''Ikinyamakuru New York Times'' cyayishyize ku rutonde rwa filime ya cumi na kabiri nziza yo mu kinyejana cya makumyabiri na rimwe . 

